msgstr "Vyzvenout CodeLite jakmile je dosaženo breakpointu"

#: LiteEditor/debuggersettingsbasedlg.cpp:415
msgid ""
"Normally, when a breakpoint is hit, you'll want CodeLite to be raise to the "
"top of the window z-order, so that you can examine values of variables etc.\n"
"However you won't always want that to happen; in particular, not if the "
"breakpoint has commands, which end in 'continue'. If so untick this box to "
"stop it happening."
msgstr ""
"Běžně po dosažení breakpointu budete po CodeLite chtít, aby zobrazil okna v "
"z-pořadí pro zobrazení proměnných atp.\n"
